title: Röda mattan eller renar?
overview: What happens when one of Sápmi's and Norway's biggest influencers and celebrities, Erlend Elias Bragstad, questions his entire family history? In the reality series Röda mattan or reindeer? he leaves his glamorous red-carpet life to find out if he really is the same - or if everything was just a family crown he and half the family have passed on.
